Page ContentHello, my name is Angela Bright and I am your school 
counselor. If you have any questions or concerns at anytime 
as relates to coursework, college, or scholarships please 
contact me at 803-419-1348, ext. 4 or via email at 
abright@richland2.org
 
 
ATTENTION ALL STUDENTS:
The South Carolina Education and Economic Development Act of 2005 (SCEEDA) requires that all students  receive career guidance. Students will complete an Individual Graduation Plan that includes courses required for graduation and a career major of their choice. Parents, guardians, or appointed representatives are invited to participate in this process. 
The meetings are scheduled daily Monday-Wednesday and Friday from 8am - 3pm and Thursday from 4pm - 7pm.  Please call the counseling department to schedule a meeting at 419-1348 option 4. 
 
 












