Charter High SchoolSchool Improvement Council

Page Content​We need your help! The School Improvement Council is a great way for parents to get involved in your child’s education! We are currently looking for parents who are interested in joining the School Improvement Council for Richland Two Charter High School. If you are interested, please contact Henry Lovett at 419-1348, or via email at hlovett@richland2.org as soon as possible.
Click here to view the SC School Improvement Council brochure
 
http://sic.sc.gov/publicationsanddownloads/Pages/DownloadSICBrochures.aspx












Richland Two Charter High School   7900 Brookmont Lane, Columbia SC  29203   Tel: (803) 419-1348  Fax: (803) 935-1212©Copyright 2015 Richland County School District Two





















