Charter High SchoolStudent Registration

Page ContentStudent Registration
If you are new to Richland School District Two, please go to https://www.richland2.org/Departments/planning/Pages/EnrollmentAnnualRegistration.aspx  to register online. All students who are new to the district must register online. 
If you have previously been enrolled in a Richland Two school, or if you are currently enrolled at a Richland Two school and would like to transfer to the charter school, please print and complete the student application. Return the application to Ms. Rebecca Cupstid. 
If you have questions, please call Ms. Cupstid at 803-419-1348 ext. 5. 












